3. cs.LG - The paper discusses the use of heuristic algorithms to program software-controlled agents, which is a common topic in machine learning. 
4. cs.ED - The paper focuses on the teaching and learning process in higher education, specifically in the field of Artificial Intelligence. 
5. cs.CY - The paper proposes a new Turing test for computer games bots based on linguistic modelling of complex phenomena, which falls under the category of cybersecurity.
